<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">
Reported from Greece as 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Syllidae" genus="Procerastea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Procerastea perrieri" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="perrieri">Procerastea perrieri</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nicolaidou, A." journalOrPublisher="Rapport et Proces-Verbaux des Reunions de la Commission Internationale pour l'Exploration Scientifique de la Mer Mediterranee" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination=": 20" title="Taxonomic and ecological study of the polychaete fauna of the N. Sporades. Aegean Sea." volume="30" year="1986">Nicolaidou et al. (1986)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Simboura, Nomiki" journalOrPublisher="Marine Ecology" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="283 - 306" title="Benthic Communities of the lnfralittoral in the N. Sporades (Aegean Sea): a Variety of Biotopes Encountered and Analysed" volume="16" year="1995">Simboura et al. (1995b)</bibRefCitation>
, subsequently listed as 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Syllidae" genus="Procerastea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Procerastea nematodes" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="nematodes">Procerastea nematodes</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Arvanitidis, Christos" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin of Marine Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="73 - 96" title="Polychaete fauna of the Aegean Sea: inventory and new information" volume="66" year="2000">Arvanitidis (2000a)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Simboura, Nomiki" journalOrPublisher="Monographs on Marine Sciences" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 115" title="The Polychaetes (Annelida, Polychaeta) of Greece: Checklist, Distribution and Ecological Characteristics" volume="4" year="2001">Simboura and Nicolaidou (2001)</bibRefCitation>
. In the Mediterranean also reported from Italy (
<bibRefCitation author="Castelli, A" journalOrPublisher="Biologia Marina Mediterranea" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="323 - 373" title="AnnelidaPolychaeta" volume="15" year="2008">Castelli et al. 2008</bibRefCitation>
), otherwise distributed along the Atlantic coasts of Europe. 
<bibRefCitation author="Nygren, Arne" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 314" title="Revision of Autolytinae (Syllidae: Polychaeta)" volume="680" year="2004">Nygren (2004)</bibRefCitation>
restricts the species' distribution to the North-East Atlantic and the North-East Pacific.
</paragraph>
